{"tid":1633844,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"今日做咩咁多風話勇武休息？","createTime":"2019-10-07T05:28:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T10:32:44.000Z","uid":63667,"like":13,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"5b7c68d5893cbe7c77867730c8ea998918f8dea2","tid":1633844,"uid":63667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:28:35.000Z","msg":"又當連登仔on9？<br />\n係人都知今晚就係要收黨鐵皮<br />\n聽日就全線被罷工<br />\n<br />\n竟然有風向撚叫人淨係唱歌<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29a4aa21ab7b6ee4d899976a541dde35c91d81fd","tid":1633844,"uid":167011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:28:49.000Z","msg":"罷工係對個政權最撚有衝擊既抗爭手法，但三罷做左咁撚多次，都係得8.5成功，因為計劃左好撚耐，對香港人黎講，個個都只想被罷工，到呢個地步，你仲想做休息撚，而唔乘勝追擊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勿拆黨鐵！！全民被罷工！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n三樣香港人應同樣憎恨既野：<br />\n政府、黑警、黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n呢三樣先係主線<br />\n你個啲乜鳩紅藍店，我理撚得你幾時搞？<br />\n個啲要休息，冇問題，但咁撚樣都唔食住上，令到全港自動罷工，咁我真係代表我全力支持既香港政府多謝你為香港既經濟服務<br />\n<br />\n唔撚係話和理非冇用，但和勇合一係成場運動既關鍵，兩樣一齊做唔撚得？講緊既係，拆鐵係唔撚會影響人權法，或所謂既民意，但對政權、運動係現時有最大既影響力"},{"pid":"c03914d63d4754a04efdf1cf6e6dda136ffcae1b","tid":1633844,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:29:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae3338a0ef13ecbaf832b83f10776e03473edc40","tid":1633844,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:29:27.000Z","msg":"我諗大家要搞清楚三點啦<br />\n<br />\n1・由始至終<span style=\"color: red;\"> 由星期五晚起 都係講星期六休息做好文宣 星期日和理非場 星期一18區行動以實行星期二大三罷效果</span><br />\n2・連登冇熄過燈 一直可以討論行動 點解之前冇人提出過星期一休息e個論點？<br />\n3・有決定後 行動當日無端端有人吹風做其他 仲反咬返堅持原定計畫既人係鬼、冇腦、唔識野<br />\n<br />\n我想問大家 邊個係鬼？堅<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">持星期一實行18區既係鬼 定吹風休息果班係鬼</span>？"},{"pid":"405ff60fa756f0d82148910071f2c69ce5af464c","tid":1633844,"uid":313341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:29:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f258ccbd65e13b068a845aac3f8df18f3b9a9a8b","tid":1633844,"uid":54524,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:30:07.000Z","msg":"已經唔撚想上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dc6f27c39f0edc88d2d2063dd7425b2ef3006f3","tid":1633844,"uid":63667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:30:35.000Z","msg":"要人手推呢個上去"},{"pid":"1b3a44382c4a14780efd516132fe33446f9cca2e","tid":1633844,"uid":270824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:31:26.000Z","msg":"推翻啲正常文上去<br />\n雖然我推唔撚到"},{"pid":"15e23962805edb366828a913178b44f0be7db678","tid":1633844,"uid":3465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:31:43.000Z","msg":"岩呀, 根本搞黨鐵又唔似裝修鋪頭咁令人反感<br />\n而香港人又係希望被罷工"},{"pid":"990e6542d0e6b9479a18c2ec3ba63d8720e255ef","tid":1633844,"uid":76078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:32:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"931b3fcbc7bffe2f5cb8b727a8f34b6b974d8c0a","tid":1633844,"uid":322508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:36:06.000Z","msg":"大家緊守崗位，記得四大原則。<br />\n<br />\n10月7日<br />\n<br />\n和理非：<br />\n1. 貼文宣 (全日)<br />\n2. 唱歌 (大家預20:00或更早)<br />\n3. 追悼會 (19:00，睇日程表)<br />\n3. 國際文宣戰線 (全日)<br />\n<br />\n勇武：<br />\n1. 只針對裝修爛鐵(睇黨鐵情況而定，可在8點或更早)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SXfkVGt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSXfkVGt.jpg&h=cf2461bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2UBoT